---
// Componente Productivity - Sección de IA y ciberprotección
---

<section class="productivity-section">
    <div class="productivity-container">
        <div class="productivity-content">
            <h2 class="productivity-title">Impulsa tu productividad con IA y ciberprotección</h2>
            <p class="productivity-description">
                Automatiza procesos en Microsoft 365, protege tu información con Acronis y transforma tu forma de trabajar con Inteligencia Artificial.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="productivity-illustration">
            <img src="/images/Group 1.webp" alt="Tecnologías de IA y ciberprotección" class="productivity-image">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Productivity Section Styles */
    .productivity-section {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(1, 7, 56, 0.8), rgba(1, 7, 56, 0.8)), url('/images/imagEnovel3.webp');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        padding: 5rem 10rem;
        position: relative;
        max-width: 100vw;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .productivity-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 3% auto;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 4rem;
    }

    .productivity-content {
        text-align: left;
        max-width: 600px;
        color: #ffffff;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .productivity-illustration {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .productivity-image {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        max-height: 400px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    .productivity-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .productivity-description {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        margin-bottom: 0;
        text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .productivity-container {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .productivity-content {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .productivity-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .productivity-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .productivity-section {
            padding: 6rem 1rem;
            background-attachment: scroll;
        }

        .productivity-container {
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .productivity-title {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }

        .productivity-description {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .productivity-section {
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
        }

        .productivity-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .productivity-description {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
    }
</style> 